title: HGB Bonuscast 1
itunes:title: HGB Bonucast 1
description: This first Bonuscast from History Goes Bump takes listeners behind the scenes and shares some outtakes from the show that were never meant to make it to air as well as some behind the scenes information. A listener also shares her tribe's beliefs when it comes to ghosts, the supernatural and...hair.  Enjoy this fun show as we welcome 2014!
